<lb n="3"/>tuḷaippoṉ patiṉkaḻañcum koṇṭu Ippoṉṉukku Iṟaiykāva(l)lāka Eṇṇūṟṟu Ai 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>mpatu <unclear>p</unclear>otti vanta Iṟaiyum Eccoṟum veṭṭiyum maṟṟum Epp(o)rpaṭṭatum cantirātittavar ti
